channel.title: Music?
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape community,
There are many RS music downloads but none of them has the old version of song named "Assault and Battery". Actually I couldn't find it anywhere on the Internet. http://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/File:Assault_and_Battery.ogg (Only a part of it but that's what I'm looking for).
I know there are tons of "old school" (2007-2009) private servers, also ones that have music. Any chances of that song still existing somewhere? Why I said 2007-2009 is because it was released in 2007 and updated in 2010.
Music is located in cache right? If someone could dump me musics from a cache from year 2008, that would be helpful too I guess.
Cheers.
